    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Those from this branch of the clan focus more on the music. The message. They support their allies and keep the music rocking all night long.</p><ul><li><strong>The Finest Booze:</strong> At 1st level, you always keep a bottle of the finest booze with you. It fuels your melancholy tunes. You gain access to the <em>Medical</em> keyword, as detailed in the <em><strong>Medical Release: Support</strong></em> Chakra Feat. You also gain proficiency in Persuasion.</li></ul>",
